## Stage 3-Infra — Infrastructure/IaC Review

*(Run whenever the diff includes infrastructure-as-code changes — Terraform, Kubernetes manifests, IAM policies, network rules, queue/topic provisioning. These carry a different risk profile than application code and are easy to under-review if treated as "just more diff.")*

```
